description: Essex police are seeking the extradition of 40-year-old Ronan Hughes from County Monaghan.
title: Essex lorry deaths: Ronan Hughes 'was organiser'
title_page: Essex lorry deaths: Ronan Hughes 'was organiser' - BBC News
maintext: A man whose extradition is being sought by Essex Police over the manslaughter of 39 Vietnamese nationals was the organiser of the criminal activity for financial gain, a court has heard.
